5:
School Visit Day? Aliksir has never
heard of such a phenomenon.
9:
Next week, Nephtim's school will
have a day for parents and
guardians to visit us and observe
our classes.
12:
Nephtim wants both of you to come.
That way, you can see how much
Nephtim is learning—and how fun
school is.
17: Aliksir would be delighted to attend.
25:
Directive added: show everyone that
Nephtim is studying hard!
29: Nephtim will be a star student!
34:
You know, Nephtim... Star students
usually do their homework.
43:
All right, is there anyone who can
solve this problem?
51:
Nephtim did her homework. The
answer is 2x + 1.
55:
Impressive! I heard math was her
least favorite subject, but she seems
to be faring well.
60:
She's studying very hard. She wants
to make everyone proud.
73:
Nephtim, you're doing great, but you
don't need to pose EVERY time you
get the answer right.
76:
A hard-working youth on the rise...
Her growth is simply un-bull-ievable!
80:
Oh, Beaucy! Are you here as one of
Nephtim's guardians, too?
84:
No, I'm here representing the BRASS
and our producer. We're sponsoring
the Show Club—to stake out prime
talent.
88:
As her sister, I made a sign to cheer
her on. But since that would be a
distraction, I've opted to cheer
silently to myself.
93:
You sound more like a fan than a
family member...
98:
Guardians. Please refrain from
talking during class.
103:
This is just the beginning of my
performance. 
Please let Nephtim cook.
107:
Shibuya's star student Nephtim has
just begun to shine!
110:
O all-devouring darkness! O grand
winds that surge through the sky!
113:
Activating Alter Device. Now
establishing golem connection.
116:
We will crush the stars with our
skills...
119:
For top students like us, this is a
breeze. A piece of cake. A walk in the
park.
124:
...However, sometimes even star
students also make mistakes.
135: Papa... Are you going home already?
138:
Not yet, Nephtim. I'll stay the night.
There is still much I want to hear
about your time at school.
141:
Coming here with you was definitely
the right decision. It has warmed my
heart to see you doing so well.
148:
How about you, Aliksir? Did you have
fun at school?
153:
This query is complicated. Aliksir
does not quite comprehend the
sensation of "fun."
155:
All Aliksir wished was to understand
the origin of Sister Nephtim's
feelings.
163: How are your loneliness levels, sister?
168:
They are lower than before, but... are
still at non-zero figures.
172:
It seems improbable to remove
loneliness entirely. This is because
everyone has to say goodbye
eventually.
176:
However, a newer, warmer
sensation has set in—likely because
everyone came to Nephtim's class.
178:
Therefore, Nephtim would estimate
that loneliness levels are currently at
3%. The remaining 97% comprises
positive emotions.
187:
In contrast, fun levels have currently
reached 150%. Nephtim wishes to
raise everyone else's fun levels as
well.
190:
That is Nephtim's treasure. And
Nephtim wants to share it with you.
193:
Nephtim is so glad she woke up.
Thank you, Stella.
198:
I'm happy you're here with us,
Nephtim.
203:
Nephtim will continue to perform
and make everyone feel warm
inside—this will be easy, because
her music is straight FIRE.
206:
However, Nephtim is just getting
started. One day, Nephtim will be
the G.O.A.T.!
216:
Uh oh... It seems Sotieth forgot to
camouflage the carrots... How is
Nephtim going to eat all of her
veggies now?
221:
I feel bad always asking for help, so I
told Sotieth not to hide the carrots
this time. I figured Nephtim could
give it a try—
237:
She... She ate her very first carrot all
on her own!
251:
New primary directive: ratio and
destroy ALL carrots. Nephtim will
never eat another yucky carrot
again.
256: Oh come on, was it really THAT bad?!
260:
Crush the carrots and shatter
adulthood. Nephtim vows to never
grow up.
